  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0bae\u0ba8\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd- ;,\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd  \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1- \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka and India are good friends - India supports constitutional democratic practices followed in Sri Lanka - Indian High Commissioner said in an interview",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The High Commissioner emphasized the importance of India to Sri Lanka, which is facing an unprecedented crisis as Sri Lanka votes to elect a new president.",
        "He said that as the Indian High Commissioner, he is focusing on ensuring stability in Sri Lanka and ensuring that the country returns to normalcy.",
        "He said that it was a privilege to represent India at any level as a diplomat and he also mentioned that he was happy that he was able to represent India in some important missions abroad.",
        "This seems like a very critical moment for Sri Lanka. Apart from the economic crisis, there is also a political dimension at this critical moment. As the Indian High Commissioner, I and my colleagues, with the guidance and assistance of the authorities in New Delhi, are trying to extend India's help and support to the people of Sri Lanka in these difficult times and to strengthen democracy, stability and economic recovery. He further stated.",
        "Both countries are soulmates Both countries are twin births Both countries are mutual in times of crisis and greatness; He also said that it is customary to help",
        "However, he refused to comment on China's disappearance at the time of crisis.",
        "The 225 members of parliament will elect a new president for the remainder of the current president's term - He said that India supports the constitutional democratic practices followed in Sri Lanka, where the problems that have arisen at the political level will be resolved through constitutional democratic processes."
      ],
